{"tid":496822,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打可以翻譯下 余與汝 遇於雨 篇文","createTime":"2017-12-12T05:57:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T07:55:21.000Z","uid":121473,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4b644c60cc3239bca7d2b2c0955e51841c524f00","tid":496822,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T05:57:57.000Z","msg":"其實成篇點解?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n余與汝 遇於雨 汝語余 於雨餘 <br />\n<br />\n於汝寓 汝娛余 汝予乳 予余娛 <br />\n<br />\n余預羽 羽娛乳 娛乳餘 汝如雨 <br />\n<br />\n余御汝 如魚愉 御汝餘 愈譽余"},{"pid":"3daeb51b0fb0955d0b011419e4d330f4fd697a73","tid":496822,"uid":134908,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T06:02:44.000Z","msg":"中學未畢業?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c885a43d1501e9489ce2dd5dd2fdcf470c8d0fdc","tid":496822,"uid":135390,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T06:17:53.000Z","msg":"甜故黎?"},{"pid":"cc515e27ebbdb651032b5edde6caed2a69214967","tid":496822,"uid":52362,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T06:31:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實成篇點解?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n余與汝 遇於雨 汝語余 於雨餘 <br />\n<br />\n於汝寓 汝娛余 汝予乳 予余娛 <br />\n<br />\n余預羽 羽娛乳 娛乳餘 汝如雨 <br />\n<br />\n余御汝 如魚愉 御汝餘 愈譽余</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我同你 相遇喺雨天 你同我講 落完雨之後<br />\n喺你屋 你俾我玩 你提供乳房 俾我玩<br />\n我預備定羽毛 掃你乳房 玩完乳房 你濕到好似落完雨咁<br />\n我騎你 你好似魚咁快樂 騎你之餘 你仲讚我"},{"pid":"e5aa2bb32ffd4029966376d248595cd3769e2a94","tid":496822,"uid":818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T06:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji